              "type": "TileTransform",
              "optional": false
            }
          ],
          "returnType": "number",
          "description": "Encode a tileset-local tile reference and transform into a packed word. The localTileId is stored as (localTileId + 1) so that a packed value of 0 cleanly represents an empty cell, while tile 0 from tileset 0 with identity transform is stored as 1 (non-zero). Returns 0 for an empty cell. Public so chunk-provider authors (e.g. a format adapter or procedural generator) can build a ChunkPayload's tiles array without duplicating this encoding."
        },
